rules.name: Rules Text
rules.text:
{i}As a siege enters, choose an opponent to protect it. You and others can attack it. When it’s defeated, exile it, then cast it transformed.{/i}
When this Siege enters, create four 1/1 colorless Droid artifact creature tokens. They gain haste until end of turn. Until end of turn, if a source you control would deal damage to a permanent, it deals twice that much damage instead.
